PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of JOCELYNE MARIE-PAULINE HOULE of Val-des-Bois, Quebec, as Chairperson of the board of directors of Canada Lands Company Limited, to hold office during pleasure for a term ending on September 30, 2022, or until such time as a new Chairperson is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective June 19, 2022.
